sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Action_role-playing_video_games> ; <http://dbpedia.org/property/ign> ?score } ORDER BY DESC(?score) LIMIT 10
